      "ConcreteType": "PythonNodeModels.PythonNode, PythonNodeModels",
      "Code": "A=IN[0]\r\nB=IN[1]\r\n\r\nS=[]\r\nfor a in A:\r\n\tif a in B:\r\n\t\tS.append(True)\r\n\telse:\r\n\t\tS.append(False)\r\nOUT=S",
